      "description": "For sale: vehicle in mint condition. The exterior is flawless with no scratches, dents, or imperfections in the paint. The interior is in pristine condition, showing no signs of wear or use on the upholstery or carpeting. All mechanical and electronic systems are in perfect working order.",
