    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver for those who value mechanical reliability over physical perfection. The engine and transmission are in good working order, and it has been regularly serviced to ensure it stays on the road. However, please note that there are visible signs of wear, including some minor exterior scratches and interior fading consistent with its age. It is a solid, functional car that is ready for its next owner.",
