      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the marque, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine with its signature individual throttle bodies and a perfectly calibrated dual-VANOS system. The valvetrain operates with factory-spec tolerances, and the rod bearings have been proactively addressed to ensure long-term mechanical integrity. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag six-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis is structurally flawless, having received a comprehensive rear subframe reinforcement to mitigate stress-induced fatigue. Suspension kinematics remain razor-sharp, utilizing OEM dampers and refreshed bushings that maintain the original factory geometry and damping rates. Finished in a concours-level exterior with zero oxidation or clear coat failure, this is a mechanically transparent, turn-key machine for the discerning collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
